# https://editorconfig.org
# Target: .NET 10 / C# 14
# Last Updated: 2026-01-04
#
# REFERENCES:
# - EditorConfig Spec: https://editorconfig.org
# - Template: https://github.com/dotnet/runtime/blob/main/.editorconfig
# - Code Style Rules: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/fundamentals/code-analysis/code-style-rule-options
