# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Reference: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/whats-new/csharp-13

# IDE0330: Prefer System.Threading.Lock (.NET 9+ / C# 13+)
# Recommends using the dedicated Lock type instead of object for synchronization.
# Provides better performance and clearer intent for thread synchronization.
