# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# INVERT IF (CRITICAL - Early Returns / Guard Clauses)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Enforces fail-fast pattern by suggesting to invert nested if statements.
# This is the most important rule for encouraging early returns and guard clauses.
